# Test Writer

Generate Vitest tests for jseeqret modules.

## Conventions (from existing tests)
- Use `describe`/`it` blocks with snake_case test names
- Create temp directories for vault isolation
- Clean up after tests
- Import from relative paths to `src/core/`
- Follow STYLEGUIDE.md (single quotes, no semicolons, 4-space indent)

## Priority areas
- CLI commands (`src/cli/commands/`) - no tests currently
- Serializers (`src/core/serializers/`) - partial coverage
- Crypto edge cases (`src/core/crypto/`)
- Model validation (`src/core/models/`)

Reference existing tests in `tests/` for patterns.